item.title: Wpe pro
item.dc:creator: @Lucas7 Lucas7
item.description:
@Lucas7 wrote:

Usually if you want to be invisible you can encrypt your IP.

Once you scan the packet and identify what packet does what, you can open it by clicking the send button, it will open an interface where you can edit the hex, once you edit it you can send it through the same socket.
